SAS Go Light


Fare without baggage allowance. Hand baggage only allowed. Valid on SAS operated flights only.

First bag can be purchased at a charge.

Changes: Rebooking is permitted at a charge of DKK/NOK/SEK 600/EUR 65 per sector/person. In case of upgrading to a higher SAS Go Light/SAS Plus fare, the difference between the fare paid and the higher fare will be added. Origin/destination may not be changed.

Refund: Ticket and domestic/international fees are non-refundable.

Child discount: 2-11 years 25% discount. 0-2 years 90% discount. No discount on taxes or fees.

SAS Plus Saver


Changes: Rebooking is permitted against DKK/NOK/SEK 600/EUR 65 per sector/person. In case of upgrading to a higher fare, the difference between the fare paid and the higher fare will be added.

Refund: Ticket is refundable against DKK/NOK/SEK 600/EUR 65 per sector/person before commencement of travel. Ticket and domestic/international fees are non-refundable after commencement of travel.

Child discount: 2-11 years 25% discount. 0-2 years 90% discount. No discount on taxes or fees.
